-- MOVES-U.S. Bancorp unit names Gregory Block as private banker
-- 
-- Mon Dec 15, 2014 11:52AM EST
-- None



Dec 15 (Reuters) - U.S. Bank Wealth Management, a unit of U.S. Bancorp <USB.N>,  appointed Gregory Block as a private banker in Milwaukee to provide specialized lending services.

He will also oversee the day-to-day management of financial activities for high-net-worth clients. Block has more than 12 years of banking and financial services experience, the company said.